WEBVTT

00:08:27.645 --> 00:08:30.390
either themselves or their families

00:08:30.414 --> 00:08:31.692
or their neighbors.

00:08:32.674 --> 00:08:36.634
One of those white Republican
women in Charlotte was a waitress

00:08:37.443 --> 00:08:41.556
struggling to stay awake
with an enormous Big Gulp soda.

00:08:41.580 --> 00:08:43.563
She just looked exhausted.

00:08:44.160 --> 00:08:45.747
And she was.

00:08:45.771 --> 00:08:47.748
She told us that she worked two jobs

00:08:47.772 --> 00:08:50.761
but still could not afford
a membership to the Y,

00:08:50.785 --> 00:08:53.874
but it was OK that she couldn't go
to the gym, she said,

00:08:53.898 --> 00:08:56.585
because she also could not afford gas

00:08:56.609 --> 00:08:59.340
and walked 10 miles to and from work

00:08:59.364 --> 00:09:00.864
every single day.